# ── Research / draft protection ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# This is a PUBLIC repo. Unpublished analysis drafts and modelling artifacts must
# never be committable here — a stray `git add -A` would leak them on github.com.
# Keep drafts in /home/julie/hormuz-report-drafts/ or a private repo; if they must
# live in this working tree for editing, these patterns keep them un-committable.
# Finished pieces are published via content/analysis/ only, never as loose files.
*.md.draft
*-draft.md
*-report-draft.md
*-spec.md
*-reconciliation.md
second-shock-*.md
monte-carlo-*.md
buffer-state-*.md
temp_docs/
newsletters/drafts/

# Cascade / Monte Carlo modelling artifacts (research, not site code)
*.py
__pycache__/
calibrated_params.json
fig_*.png
*:Zone.Identifier
